Implemented all eight H14 fixes and wrote the required report at [.review-slices/H14.fix.md](/Users/williamcory/tevm-monorepo/.review-slices/H14.fix.md).

Touched only in-scope package files plus the requested report. Key changes: fixed recursive resolution queuing, preserved/reused resolved import metadata, rewrote module imports while keeping `raw_code`, fixed remapping joins and the commented-import heuristic, added runtime ABI formatting and bytecode inclusion, aligned `generateRuntimeJs` shape/signature, and made solc output-selected fields optional.

I did not run tests or builds, per the hard constraints.
